ygData.subject: Re: pp gp sp cp. why dont I have any?
ygData.msgSnippet: No it, the closest city is Riverdale. So goto Riverdale, then make you way from Misty Thicket to Runnyeye dungeon, enter the dungeon stick right until you zone
ygData.messageBody:
No it, the closest city is Riverdale.

So goto Riverdale, then make you way from Misty Thicket to Runnyeye dungeon,
enter the dungeon stick right until you zone -BOOM- you have entered the
gorge of King Xorbb (or Beholders Maze). You should be able to find a group
there to join, DO NOT try and kill a gorge with just 2 level 9 people, you
will die. Gorge minotaurs are about level 14 or 15.

Jaade.
